description: Welcome to Unit 36 at Dahlgren Hall, a professionally managed, elevator building in the heart of Southie. Spanning over 1300+ sq ft, featuring 2 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. The open-concept living area includes a chef's kitchen with Thermador appliances and a large island with a beverage fridge, perfect for entertaining. The bedroom wing houses a guest room with a marble-tiled bath and a king-sized primary suite with a spa-like bathroom, double vanity and walk-in closet. Additional perks include central A/C, in-unit laundry, massive extra storage room, and 2 garage spaces. Enjoy the sweeping roof deck and a common club room that includes a kitchenette and bathroom. Conveniently located near vibrant West Broadway, it offers easy access to restaurants, cafes, grocery stores, retail, parks, highways, and public transportation.
